          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "104ed18d",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2>Commercial Tile\u00a0&amp;\u00a0Grout Cleaning\u00a0That Revives Your Floors</h2><p data-start=\"63\" data-end=\"224\">Over time, dirt, grease, and contaminants seep into porous grout lines and textured tile surfaces, dulling your floor\u2019s appearance and creating hygiene concerns.</p><p data-start=\"226\" data-end=\"388\">At Midland Floor Care, we specialize in commercial tile and grout cleaning that brings back a like-new look and helps extend the life of your flooring investment.</p><p data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"448\"><strong data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"448\">Why businesses need professional tile &amp; grout cleaning</strong></p><ul data-start=\"449\" data-end=\"761\"><li data-start=\"449\" data-end=\"528\"><p data-start=\"451\" data-end=\"528\">Restores original appearance: eliminates discoloration and uneven grout tones</p></li><li data-start=\"529\" data-end=\"604\"><p data-start=\"531\" data-end=\"604\">Improves hygiene: removes bacteria, mold, and allergens from porous grout</p></li><li data-start=\"605\" data-end=\"684\"><p data-start=\"607\" data-end=\"684\">Protects your investment: helps prevent grout erosion and costly replacements</p></li><li data-start=\"685\" data-end=\"761\"><p data-start=\"687\" data-end=\"761\">Maintains brand standards: keeps your space looking sharp and professional</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"763\" data-end=\"811\"><strong data-start=\"763\" data-end=\"811\">Our commercial tile &amp; grout cleaning process</strong></p><ol data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"1204\"><li data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"897\"><p data-start=\"815\" data-end=\"897\">Inspection and assessment: identify stains, discoloration, and high-traffic wear</p></li><li data-start=\"898\" data-end=\"971\"><p data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"971\">Pre-treatment: professional solutions loosen soil and embedded grime</p></li><li data-start=\"972\" data-end=\"1048\"><p data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"1048\">Agitation: specialized brushes scrub grout lines for deeper penetration</p></li><li data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1121\"><p data-start=\"1052\" data-end=\"1121\">Hot water extraction: high pressure and suction remove contaminants</p></li><li data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1204\"><p data-start=\"1125\" data-end=\"1204\">Grout sealing (recommended): protects against future staining and discoloration</p></li></ol><p data-start=\"1206\" data-end=\"1229\"><strong data-start=\"1206\" data-end=\"1229\">Industries we serve</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1420\"><li data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1262\"><p data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1262\">Restaurants and food service</p></li><li data-start=\"1263\" data-end=\"1301\"><p data-start=\"1265\" data-end=\"1301\">Retail stores and shopping centers</p></li><li data-start=\"1302\" data-end=\"1344\"><p data-start=\"1304\" data-end=\"1344\">Office buildings and corporate lobbies</p></li><li data-start=\"1345\" data-end=\"1367\"><p data-start=\"1347\" data-end=\"1367\">Hotels and resorts</p></li><li data-start=\"1368\" data-end=\"1393\"><p data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1393\">Healthcare facilities</p></li><li data-start=\"1394\" data-end=\"1420\"><p data-start=\"1396\" data-end=\"1420\">Educational institutions</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1422\" data-end=\"1466\"><strong data-start=\"1422\" data-end=\"1466\">Why businesses choose Midland Floor Care</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1467\" data-end=\"1692\"><li data-start=\"1467\" data-end=\"1522\"><p data-start=\"1469\" data-end=\"1522\">Commercial expertise: solutions for high-use spaces</p></li><li data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1575\"><p data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1575\">Advanced equipment: deeper, longer-lasting clean</p></li><li data-start=\"1576\" data-end=\"1633\"><p data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1633\">Flexible service hours: nights and weekends available</p></li><li data-start=\"1634\" data-end=\"1692\"><p data-start=\"1636\" data-end=\"1692\">Guaranteed results: backed by our Midland Shine Standard</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1722\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you,<br data-start=\"1704\" data-end=\"1707\" />Justin Campbell</p><p data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1722\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><strong><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your On-Site Visit</a></strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your Visit &amp; Quote</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/ultimate-guide-to-floor-care-for-retail/\">Ultimate Guide to Floor Care for Retail</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/jobs/\">Jobs</a></li></ul>",
                "align": "left",
